description: Mama Bee's bright yellow truck is hard to miss! Classing up the concept of a hot dog cart, Mama Bee's cooks delicious hot dogs with a variety of traditional and exciting toppings. You could go with the classic Chicago dog or get some New Mexico flavors with red or green on top. Not in the mood for a dog? Get some enchiladas, a tortilla burger or a quesadilla.
name: Mama Bee's Cuisine and Catering
